7f3e0853461733b7054babdead597cbe2c00ce28a3e2d77a7380fa657009bc05ea5eb5637054bbf3f33e5f8315f95227173ad0999c90b3bb621511e3c9a77a53  0001-update-kernel-support-more-System.map-and-config-fil.patch
"
